        "kind": "pull_request",
        "title": "fix: clear timeout timer in Nostr profile relay publish loop",
        "body": "Related: #98463\n\n## What Problem This Solves\n\nFixes an issue where each Nostr relay publish would leave a dangling timer after `Promise.race` completed.\n\n## Why This Change Was Made\n\nWrap the per-relay `Promise.race` in `try/finally` that clears the timer handle.\n\n## User Impact\n\nNo user-visible change. Prevents a minor timer leak when publishing Nostr profiles.\n\n## Evidence\n\nRuntime verification (fix/timer-leak-nostr, rebased on upstream/main 6495358f):\n\n```\nnostr-profile.test.ts — Test Files 1 passed, Tests 31 passed\n✓ profileToContent > converts full profile to NIP-01 content\n✓ createProfileEvent > creates a valid kind:0 event\n✓ createProfileEvent > produces a verifiable signature\n... (31/31 ✓, Duration 1.54s)\n```\n\n[test] passed 1 Vitest shard.",
